article:
This article lists 'National Historic Landmarks in New York City', of which
there are 112. One of the New York City (NYC) sites is also a National Monument,
and there are two more National Monuments in NYC as well. These are listed
further below. It also briefly discusses NYC designated landmarks.

In all of New York State there are 259 National Historic Landmarks (NHLs), which
is the most of any state. For a discussion of state NHLs inside and outside of
NYC, see List of NHLs in New York State. For consistency, the sites are named
here as designated under the National Historic Landmark program.
